# Deep Research Configuration

**Full Documentation**: @details/RESEARCH_CONFIG.md (load on-demand)

## Core Defaults

```yaml
research_defaults:
  planning_strategy: unified
  max_hops: 5
  confidence_threshold: 0.7
  memory_enabled: true
  parallelization: true
  parallel_first: true  # MANDATORY DEFAULT
  sequential_override_requires_justification: true

parallel_execution_rules:
  DEFAULT_MODE: PARALLEL  # EMPHASIZED

  mandatory_parallel:
    - "Multiple search queries"
    - "Batch URL extractions"
    - "Independent analyses"
    - "Non-dependent hops"

  sequential_only_with_justification:
    - reason: "Explicit dependency"
    - reason: "Resource constraint"
    - reason: "User requirement"

  parallel_optimization:
    batch_sizes: {searches: 5, extractions: 3, analyses: 2}
    intelligent_grouping: {by_domain: true, by_complexity: true}
```

## Planning Strategies

```yaml
planning_only:
  clarification: false
  execution: immediate

intent_planning:
  clarification: true
  max_questions: 3
  execution: after_clarification

unified:
  clarification: optional
  plan_presentation: true
  user_feedback: true
  execution: after_confirmation
```

## Research Depth Profiles

```yaml
quick: {max_sources: 10, max_hops: 1, time_limit: 2min, confidence_target: 0.6}
standard: {max_sources: 20, max_hops: 3, time_limit: 5min, confidence_target: 0.7}
deep: {max_sources: 40, max_hops: 4, time_limit: 8min, confidence_target: 0.8}
exhaustive: {max_sources: 50+, max_hops: 5, time_limit: 10min, confidence_target: 0.9}
```

## Tool Coordination

```yaml
tool_coordination:
  discovery_primary: tavily
  extraction_smart_routing: true
  reasoning_engine: sequential
  memory_backend: serena
  parallel_tool_calls: true
```

## Quick Reference

**Source Credibility**: 4-tier system (0.9-1.0 = academic/official, 0.3-0.5 = forums/blogs)
**Hop Patterns**: Entity expansion, concept deepening, temporal progression, causal chain
**Extraction Routing**: Tavily (static), Playwright (dynamic), Context7 (docs), Native (local)
**Replanning Triggers**: Confidence <0.6, time >70%, contradictions >30%
**Output Formats**: Summary (500 words), Report (detailed), Academic (formal)

For complete details see @details/RESEARCH_CONFIG.md
